channel.title: RsBot/PowerBot
channel.description:
I orginally got my Bot from RsBot, but I think RsBot is PowerBot. Ok now that's over with, I was wondering does anyone elses Bot work? I mean, I click run and the auth appears but not the password protection. It's been like this for about 2-3 days and it says on PowerBot the problem, however some people can still can get on and use it, a fix to it was to re-install.
Does anyone know how to fix this? - I tryed re-installing.
